title: Embraer makes large purchase of jets in the third quarter of 2015
text:
Embraer makes large purchase of jets in the third quarter of 2015   
Oct 15, 2015 eTN   
During the third quarter of 2015 (3Q15), Embraer delivered 21 jets to the commercial aviation market and 30 to the business aviation market, for a total of 51 aircraft. The number is 50% higher than in the same period last year, when 34 aircraft were delivered - 19 commercial and 15 executive jets.
